Svagare vindar sänker Arise elproduktion
Vindkraftsbolaget Arise elproduktion under oktober uppgick till 26,2 gigawattimmar, vilket var en bit under bolagets egen budget för månaden som var på 33,3 gigawattimmar.
06 Nov 2019, 16:09 by Nyhetsbyrån Direkt

Weaker winds lower Arise's electricity generation
The wind power company Arise's electricity generation in October amounted to 26.2 gigawatt hours, which was slightly below the company's own budget for the month, which was 33.3 gigawatt hours.
06 Nov 2019, 16:09 by News Agency Direct
